有钱能买鬼推磨，胖子看见了别人的家信。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"ec95433deb","type":"paragraph","text":"乌乎，宪法上的通信秘密权在西师只值三元多钱。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"0767d970be","type":"subtitle","text":"二、借虎作威的团支部","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"003f3017a8","type":"paragraph","text":"不论新民主主义青年团或共产主义青年团的章程上，我都未见团有领导青年的职权。其他法律上也没有这项规定。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"448f5cff7e","type":"paragraph","text":"怪哉，团支书尽是班三角之一角了。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"1f7f148b27","type":"paragraph","text":"我要问你：支书先生，我们谁请你来领导大家的？清醒些你还是党？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"f248358e66","type":"paragraph","text":" (原载“平民报”)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"fce35b2582","type":"subtitle","text":"平民报发刊词    谭家驹","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"46a3622947","type":"paragraph","text":"(原编者按：此为谭第一次宣布的带煽动性的斗争纲领)","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"2b933fa5d2","type":"paragraph","text":"生物系一年级的同学是一支迟到的队伍，但是要谈的问题是多的。你听是他们在高呼：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"71aa73a6d2","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是一群庶民，我们是黄河的子孙。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"b3cb59bc1c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是徒手的勇士，我们的热血奔腾！","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"224f28ea6b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们是黄帝的忠实儿女，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"3433689972","type":"paragraph","text":"为了民族的民主自由，(按：照谭家驹后来的解释是在“社会主义基础上建立英国式的民主”)","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"},{"id":"273d671495","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不惜任何牺牲！！！","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743"}],"page":{"id":"85dd43d7f6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ddcc772743","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}